 (* Write a function to find the occurrence and position of the substrings within a string. Return None if there is no match. *)
let rec find_substrings s =
  let rec helper s =
    if String.length s < 2 then return None
    else if String.length s = 2 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 3 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 4 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 5 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 6 then return Some (s, 0)

  let rec helper s =
    if String.length s < 2 then return None
    else if String.length s = 2 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 3 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 4 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 5 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 6 then return Some (s, 0)

    else if String.length s = 9 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 10 then return Some (s, 0)

    else if String.length s = 12 then return Some (s, 0)

    else if String.length s = 15 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 16 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 17 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 18 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 19 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 20 then return Some (s, 0)
    else if String.length s = 21 then return Some (s, 0)
